Lumen's Windows desktop application uses Slint 1.13.1 under the Slint
Royalty-free Desktop, Mobile, and Web Applications License 2.0. The application
provides the required AboutSlint attribution in its top-level About screen.

Lumen links Opus for low-latency audio encoding under its BSD 3-Clause license
and includes ViGEmClient under the MIT License. The shared UI icons are selected
from Tabler Icons under the MIT License. Complete license texts are installed or
bundled with the application. `Rust-Crates.html` lists the Rust dependency graph,
crate versions, selected license expressions, and detected license texts.
